{"tid":562273,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解個撚個都話新年要剪頭髮","createTime":"2018-02-15T17:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T04:42:01.000Z","uid":60423,"like":17,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0e46eba68dc7eaf50093e16c5681a1d506a6a985","tid":562273,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T17:50:01.000Z","msg":"上年紀嘅老一輩可以話9成9都叫你新年前一定要剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然我唔剪佢都吹我唔漲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最近發現身邊唔少90後都係到話<br />\n新年梗係剪個新頭髮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩年30趕得切剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新年剪髮加價真係明搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自中學懂事以來已經唔理依啲on99傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家覺唔覺依種風氣不可長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全體現左種中國人古老 封建 守舊 迷信嘅想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba56d4f2ff0f4983d62511e8a7f218f21a7aeabd","tid":562273,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"加多句<br />\n所以想問下大家去開邊間剪髮可以推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f4f20d7540e15c082ecf0eeda868141aa7e71f","tid":562273,"uid":32464,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T17:53:57.000Z","msg":"外觀黎講，剪完頭髮，啲分叉/白頭髮 剪晒，比較整齊 感覺係「新」<br />\n意頭黎講 ，唔想新年先黎剪「發」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef8ad1a014bd7c4fb440eb3553dc1aacae99430","tid":562273,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"